{
  "stem": "22447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they, they put these in the boxes, giving the people the impression that they're going to get it back one day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they had no intention of giving back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it shows you how thorough the Germans were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we, we're opening these envelopes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And all they had, the-- as far as the good watches-- was gone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was pocket watches, hunter watches.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were all hunter watches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I come across a few watches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "One was a Longines.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I knew a Longines or Omega was a good watch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I took a couple of watches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And while I was doing this, a fellow came in, all excited.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he shouted, it's all over!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It's all over!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The war's all over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Germany is going to sign unconditional surrender tomorrow afternoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there ?] [? will be ?] [? peace. ?] And no one lifted their head up to say anything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "See, everybody carried on looking, that they were-- see what they could find in these watches.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There was hundreds there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then, when we went out, somebody told us, someone just came and said, oh, the war's over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It's all finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But we said-- we couldn't wear those watches because knowing where they come from in Plaszow, you couldn't possibly wear them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So we just took them as souvenirs as if to say, but if we don't take them, somebody else will come along and take them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So we took a few each.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But I've still-- I gave a few-- I donated to the Sternberg Centre here in London.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And one, I've still got, a pocket watch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It's a stopwatch, does perfect time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I've still got that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- mainly, the information room, and also patrols at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The curfew was 11:00.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
